With commentary from Sterling `Steelo' Brim and Chanel (the rapping receptionist from `Fantasy Factory'), Dyrdek breaks down the clips by putting them in such categories as `Hot Mess, Worst Case Scenario, Redneck Good Times, and What Happened Last Night'.
